LoLSnakes
===========
An enhanced LoL shield for the purpose of implementing a snakes game.

This project contains the working material for a two day secondary school
Arduino workshop.

Directories:
============
|
+-Hardware              - Everything needed to build the LoLSnakes shield
|
+-Software              - Source files of the LoLSnakes shields firmware
|
+-Workshop              - Workshop materials

